      value: -0.935
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 114294877277737130, guid: 8b4e2585213011e43ab04d70f15e3a8a,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: bodyText
      value: "I pray no other mortal has to read this letter, for that would mean
        I am not the last to fall into the deceit of that man-like beast, Dracula.
        My days of desperation are coming to an end, whether that be as free man
        or a dead one, I do not know.\n\r\nI have lost count of the days I've spent
        in this room collecting dust and losing sleep. Every morning I watch the
        sun rise over the bridge that leads away from this wretched place and go
        mad, I can stay here no longer. \n\r\nI've chiseled away at the stone walls
        and found an old wooden chute of sorts. For transporting or stowing things
        away, I suppose. It's looks as it's been out of use for longer than I've
        been alive.\n\r\nThe path out of this room lies behind the wardrobe.\r\nMay
        luck be on our side\r\n"
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 114294877277737130, guid: 8b4e2585213011e43ab04d70f15e3a8a,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: isFullScreen
      value: 1
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
